status_log.map: function(doc) {        if ( doc.type != 'agent_partial' || typeof doc.account_id == 'undefined' | typeof doc.agent_id == 'undefined' ) return;        emit([doc.agent_id, doc.timestamp], doc.status);      }

call_log.map: function(doc) {        if ( (doc.type != 'call_partial' && doc.type != 'agent_partial') || typeof doc.account_id == 'undefined' | typeof doc.agent_id == 'undefined' ) return;        emit([doc.timestamp, doc.agent_id], doc.status);      }
